data.description: Owner made this house her home. She maintained this beautiful property adding her own touch including paint, some minor upgrades including the bathroom and kitchen faucets, all of the toilets, new central air conditioning system and removed all carpet replacing with hardwood floors on the second floor. This home has a nice size kitchen open to the the day room. A large master bedroom which has trey ceilings, crown molding and a sitting room. It also has a large master bath with a separate shower, jacuzzi tub with jets, double vanity and a large walk-in closet. The master bath boasts 12 foot ceilings. A nice size back yard and landscaped beautifully in the front. A new garage door opener and new mailbox. All agents bring your offers! This house wont sit long!
